{"id": 879, "genre": 1001, "title": "你讨厌哪种“教你做人”？", "description": "每天都有无数环绕立体声噪音教我做人，很累。", "record_count": 4987, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160703152331N9gpoUdwj8tZzIGx.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-03-22T11:39:58Z", "options": [{"id": 60416, "content": "最讨厌的就是有一些人爱以自己的生活方式来要求别人，啊，你应该去这样，啊，你应该去这样，真想对这种人说，滚，你应该去死！", "image": null, "praise_count": 693, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 506043}, {"id": 60672, "content": "操你爸爸", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 523504}, {"id": 60928, "content": "自己都不如我  还说我", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 530016}, {"id": 60417, "content": "各种以自己的生活方式来当作标准，只要你按照他的标准，都定义为Low，然后还要让你向他学习，不学习就是low", "image": null, "praise_count": 182, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 506043}, {"id": 60673, "content": "什么事情都推给我还对我指手画脚的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 519636}, {"id": 61697, "content": "非父母", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 534896}, {"id": 60418, "content": "买日货以后被微博朋友圈教育", "image": null, "praise_count": 152, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 346805}, {"id": 60674, "content": "被垃圾说教", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 526662}, {"id": 60419, "content": "结尾附带一句“等你长大你就明白了”，谁特么明白啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 426, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 429917}, {"id": 60675, "content": "大家說的都挺討厭的⋯⋯看得我一點怒氣都沒有了⋯⋯", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 524571}, {"id": 60420, "content": "先賺錢，再理想。", "image": null, "praise_count": 65, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 527475}, {"id": 60676, "content": "最讨厌道德绑架", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 508008}, {"id": 60421, "content": "“你这样不行”  “你不能这么做”  “像你这样根本成功不了”   说这些话的人没有意识到你这些行为也是错误的吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 69, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 527471}, {"id": 60677, "content": "每次做设计被傻逼老师妈的狗血淋头说审美层次，，，然后把作业做成傻逼老师要的样子。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 403368}, {"id": 62213, "content": "对于教我做人的人 我谢谢你们大爷", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147051}, {"id": 60422, "content": "b站史学政治家有些也是神烦，你不同意他的观点就强行说你不爱国", "image": null, "praise_count": 120, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 228770}, {"id": 60423, "content": "所有用“我跟你说这事你得听我的”“哎呀你不懂”“你还小”之类开头的以及“分分钟教你做人”结尾的话 噢 我活了这么大年纪要你来教？", "image": "img/option/option/20160703152302Ldg2yShD8JRNiqaO.jpg", "praise_count": 260, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 274056}, {"id": 60679, "content": "心靈雞湯", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 458051}, {"id": 61191, "content": "我是过来人，你们想的我都懂，我都经历过。对此我只想说呵呵", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 532000}, {"id": 61703, "content": "她/他还小，你大了让着她点呗", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 518477}, {"id": 60680, "content": "找个差不多的就行了！别挑剔了！这不怪你难道还怪社会吗？！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 528718}, {"id": 60425, "content": "自己都做不好还在那瞎BB", "image": null, "praise_count": 539, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 527481}, {"id": 60681, "content": "马后炮型～", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 447826}, {"id": 60426, "content": "教导我们为已拥有的事物感到满足这样的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 40, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 162962}, {"id": 60682, "content": "嘴里说着“教你做人”实际上是“双重标准”", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 496528}, {"id": 60427, "content": "谁知道教我做人的那人自己混的如何了...", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 331384}, {"id": 60683, "content": "最讨厌家人说：你看看人家！Grrrrrrrrrr！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 528763}, {"id": 60430, "content": "我今天是作为一个长者，向你们传授一些人生经验", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 281353}, {"id": 60431, "content": "我当年怎么怎么样，我都是经历过的，你小年轻要听长辈的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 53, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 465575}, {"id": 60432, "content": "咄咄逼人地发表狭隘的观点还不让人插嘴", "image": null, "praise_count": 98, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 448499}, {"id": 60433, "content": "自己输说的话分分钟被打脸", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 352556}, {"id": 61969, "content": "做人要有理想啊！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1284389}, {"id": 60434, "content": "律人不律己那种", "image": null, "praise_count": 368, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 522012}, {"id": 60435, "content": "我从未见过有如此厚颜无耻之人！", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 179207}, {"id": 61203, "content": "  当我做得好的时候，她觉得不好。当她做时，她自己的不足一切都成为好的了……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 499266}, {"id": 60436, "content": "女孩子就应该找份稳定的工作，嫁人比什么都重要，你看谁谁嫁得好一辈子不愁", "image": null, "praise_count": 642, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 527496}, {"id": 64276, "content": "你看看别人……我认识的一个人家的小孩……那人家怎么就吧啦吧啦……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 515098}, {"id": 60437, "content": "我要工作", "image": "img/option/option/20160606144945sRDrYvmpjn6bxL3c.gif", "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 509783}, {"id": 60438, "content": "各种装外宾，秀优越感", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 179207}, {"id": 60950, "content": "真的么", "image": "img/option/option/20160606144950FyNlAV59eIiYazRJ.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 93004}, {"id": 61974, "content": "开句就是“不是，我跟你讲..”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 517010}, {"id": 60439, "content": "不懂装懂，满脸正义的指导你的工作生活", "image": null, "praise_count": 66, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 179207}, {"id": 63255, "content": "你没到我这岁数", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 515393}, {"id": 60441, "content": "总是自作聪明，会一点东西就在那自以为是的指点别人，好像自己是什么人物", "image": null, "praise_count": 35, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 152325}, {"id": 60442, "content": "“这个太简单了，我就不说了”。每次听完后都觉得自己真是too young too naive", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 419410}, {"id": 60443, "content": "你已经很幸福了，我那个时候…（强行打断）", "image": null, "praise_count": 58, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 459593}, {"id": 61467, "content": "现在不处对象，不结婚，以后更不好找了，在以后只能找二婚的了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 510947}, {"id": 60445, "content": "什么男人要疼女人的这种“喊麦”就是sb", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 91804}, {"id": 60446, "content": "只可意会不可言传 分分钟立Flag", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 522768}, {"id": 60447, "content": "我这么做是为你好", "image": null, "praise_count": 105, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 458087}]}